<div class="center jumbotron">
  <h1>Rosecrucian Annual Period Calculator</h1>
  <p> Enter the birth month, birth day and year of interest in the 
      fields below.</p>
  <br>
  <%= form_for @rosecrucian do |f| %>
    <%= f.label :month %>
    <%= f.text_field :month %>

    <%= f.label :day %>
    <%= f.text_field :day %>

    <%= f.label :year %>
    <%= f.text_field :year %>

    <%= f.submit %>
  <% end %>
  <br><br>
  <p> Enter the data in the following form: Numeric only, MM for Month, DD 
      for Day, and YYYY for Year, where MM is in the range of 01 - 12, 
      DD is in the range of 01 - 31, and YYYY is any valid 4 digit year. </p>
  <br><br>
  <%= image_tag("SMILE.jpg", alt: "Smiley Face") %>
</div>

